{"tid":1385550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［構思］綜合助養計劃 救救香港孩子 3大項目 定期回報","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T15:30:22.000Z","uid":146717,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"caba44d2dcd515b74904bc7e629a1d9717e879e4","tid":1385550,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:04:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">綜合助養計劃構思源於近日社會中出現一群山區青年，在爬山活動後無法得到溫飽、部分青年更被困山頭；甚至被野狗啃走。<br />\n<br />\n我們作為社會另一方的較富裕一群，有社會責任解決山區青年的貧困危機，更有責任保障爬山活動的安全。<br />\n<br />\n參與對象：<br />\n1）因某些原因無法爬山但仍支持活動的人；<br />\n2）有責任感、抱負去保護山區青年的人<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">草案項目一：購買食物卷（如麥當勞禮品券/大家樂現金券）</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n目的：短期內有效解決山區青年糧食問題，不直接派發現金有兩個原因；一，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我們不是在施捨他們，而是在幫助他們，如果我們直接派發現金，青年心中難免有所負擔和內疚感，內心或會感到不舒服</strong></span>；二，直接派發現金會受外人質疑動機，容易受到三毛曲解原意。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">草案項目二：購買山區裝備（如頭盔/防毒配件）</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n目的：現時野狗戰術升級，更遭人懷疑牠們被分配了過期狗糧，該狗糧呈劇毒，山區青年一旦接觸，生命或因此受到威脅，因此山區極需要有關物資作保護人命之用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">草案項目三：綜合資金</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n目的：此為多元項目的資金，包括人道援助被啃走的青年、以及針對當時社會事件而對青年作出支援。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">回報草案：週邊產品</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n目的：就好似買愛心券咁，我們會定期將可用資源撥出作文宣及週邊產品以作回報，包括月曆、名信片、T恤等等，這些產品將於各區連濃牆免費派發，你可以選擇放在家中警惕自己勿忘初衷，抑或將它們寄畀外國親戚好友。目的是希望自己、香港人、全世界，也不會忘記香港的今天，歷史將為今天的香港留一席位。<br />\n<br />\n預覧：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rimyc8y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frimyc8y.png&h=85f04d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jsZDpff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjsZDpff.png&h=0e9ef5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是次我們計劃的助養項目純粹出於自願形式，有關細節希望各位手足討論。<br />\n<br />\n此「城」危急存亡之秋，望港人放下成見，齊心協力，守護我城。"},{"pid":"f86dc07572bbd310995ab31b92764990c79a1c83","tid":1385550,"uid":163938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61e86cc975f0b09e6c759f4c86a948051210d3e","tid":1385550,"uid":85574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:06:44.000Z","msg":"第一時間支持，點參加"},{"pid":"c4a7d5b2bc07b81739ade337e0b7849203f2fb07","tid":1385550,"uid":163938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"理念唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf66cf37a325d113720e5a630af122e8610989c","tid":1385550,"uid":104834,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n建議回報草案唔好整周邊，好易畀人覺得消費運動<br />\n而且對家長嚟講，小朋友齊整食飽返屋企已係最大回報"},{"pid":"2b391a63df2f9556efea3e3a87779b3e69e2e271","tid":1385550,"uid":201721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"07d746aac6a935eee1f6baeb700d5422e44a0eba","tid":1385550,"uid":291093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4079f51553b2f7015a4da470b4259e38522a3f91","tid":1385550,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:12:26.000Z","msg":"唔建議做統籌cap一舊錢出黎<br />\n去中心化相熟嘅人私下夾錢做就得<br />\n一做大會多左好多好多不必要嘅成本，可能反而唔係咁有效率同有效<br />\n<br />\n週邊不了，唔好再嘉年華化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4d937bd3d364c6b2ff26e7f602d5cbb7361cfe","tid":1385550,"uid":68192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"寧願tg 開channel搞，保障大家私隱"},{"pid":"fa444e65e22054cd25a4c2dd8e7bd0b11b5f5418","tid":1385550,"uid":190573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"發夢時擺d飯團喺物資站，俾肚餓嘅人食咪得囉。最貴嘅係裝備，同樣擺喺物資站，搵人幫手睇下前線有咩缺，搵人塞俾佢地就夠<br />\n<br />\n唔需要搞到太複雜"},{"pid":"3b25ec73095836dfdf8ad897edb37d0429bd674e","tid":1385550,"uid":140218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"全力支持<br />\n<br />\n但要提防唔好搞咗個大台出嚟,<br />\n同埋唔好俾人感覺班後生出嚟示威係有錢收"},{"pid":"215abd6692d9fd6675df3d3767b45234f0ed2007","tid":1385550,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf66cf37a325d113720e5a630af122e8610989c","tid":1385550,"uid":104834,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n建議回報草案唔好整周邊，好易畀人覺得消費運動<br />\n而且對家長嚟講，小朋友齊整食飽返屋企已係最大回報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"其實都係，我會諗下點樣答謝大家"},{"pid":"cd911b524ea61f9182cd9392ce14e1f4a9372048","tid":1385550,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b391a63df2f9556efea3e3a87779b3e69e2e271","tid":1385550,"uid":201721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b399ebc6ac3bf3b7becd1e01b8ea8c3d9687c0d","tid":1385550,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d746aac6a935eee1f6baeb700d5422e44a0eba","tid":1385550,"uid":291093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddda8470b471b1269867b9c70663c55e324219df","tid":1385550,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4079f51553b2f7015a4da470b4259e38522a3f91","tid":1385550,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:12:26.000Z","msg":"唔建議做統籌cap一舊錢出黎<br />\n去中心化相熟嘅人私下夾錢做就得<br />\n一做大會多左好多好多不必要嘅成本，可能反而唔係咁有效率同有效<br />\n<br />\n週邊不了，唔好再嘉年華化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"依方面我都有諗過，圍內搞一向都有<br />\n<br />\n當前最大問題有啲人因為唔同因素（例如家庭/工作）唔方便爬山，身邊可能又無乜朋友，想支持又唔知可以點支持<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂如果自己搞，到時又會搞到我好似為咗cap錢咁，所以我先整「回報項目」，取諸運動，用諸運動，最大原因就係唔想俾人覺得我為咗cap錢<br />\n<br />\n我諗緊有咩方法平衡依個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be77e5cec79d22c4de6d7271fc25c607653c5ff","tid":1385550,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b25ec73095836dfdf8ad897edb37d0429bd674e","tid":1385550,"uid":140218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"全力支持<br />\n<br />\n但要提防唔好搞咗個大台出嚟,<br />\n同埋唔好俾人感覺班後生出嚟示威係有錢收"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:07:04.000Z","msg":"所以我都唔prefer直接畀現金，應該針對某一件事幫，好似醫生咁對症下藥，唔可以次次開抗生素就算，現金就等於抗生素，太多反效果"},{"pid":"3dc83daaa0ff8a10f98d154d32a604574ab5b27f","tid":1385550,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"屌你只係識蝦細路仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKtwKKS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKtwKKS.png&h=273fb698&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b136d3877eb3e5b8a4490c882763a75a14a7db8","tid":1385550,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係唔想課， 你完全無講用咩方法去派發，呢個位好重要</span>"}]}